<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes"/>
  <title>FAQ - Frequently Asked Questions</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.6.1/css/font-awesome.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      color: #f0f0f0;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      padding-top: 80px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #333;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    h1, h2 {
      color: #f0ad4e;
    }
    p, ul {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    a {
      color: #f0ad4e;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      color: #ec971f;
    }
    .faq-section {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .faq-section h3 {
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #444;
      color: #f0ad4e;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .faq-answer {
      display: none;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      background-color: #222;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    footer {
      background-color: #333;
      padding: 20px 0;
      color: #f0f0f0;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: auto;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2em;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  
  <div class="faq-section">
    <h3>What services does Quantrex Research Inc offer?</h3>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>We offer a variety of services, including software development, AI and machine learning, cloud solutions, and technology consulting. We focus on research-driven, innovative solutions to solve modern business challenges.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-section">
    <h3>How can I contact Quantrex Research Inc?</h3>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>You can reach out to us via our <a href="/contact">contact page</a> or send us an email at support@quantrex.com. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 24-48 hours.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-section">
    <h3>Do you provide custom software solutions?</h3>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>Yes! We specialize in creating custom software tailored to the unique needs of your business. Our solutions are scalable and flexible, ensuring they grow with your business.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-section">
    <h3>What industries do you serve?</h3>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>We work with a variety of industries, including healthcare, finance, e-commerce, and more. Our versatile team can adapt to the specific requirements of any industry.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2024 Quantrex Research Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

<script>
  // FAQ Toggle Script
  const faqSections = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-section h3');
  faqSections.forEach(section => {
    section.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const answer = section.nextElementSibling;
      answer.style.display = answer.style.display === 'block' ? 'none' : 'block';
    });
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>
